tors are achievable for a LIV breaking energy\nscale $\\lesssim 2\\times 10^{29}$~eV ($\\lesssim 4\\times 10^{21}$~eV) for the\nlinear (quadratic) modification of the dispersion relation. A more simple\nexplanation would be a misidentification of a charged cosmic-ray air shower.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 16:52:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2022 12:12:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2023 10:20:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-26"}
