-similar profile and prove stable nearly\nself-similar blowup of the 2D Boussinesq and 3D Euler equations with smooth\ninitial data and boundary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 17:13:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Oct 2022 17:54:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 May 2023 17:50:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
