e$-algebra and DT are\ngeneral mathematical tools that can be used to analyze other cloud-based\nnetworks. Simulation results reveal the exactness of our analytical results and\nthe efficiency of our methodology in terms of acceptance and success rates of\nCI-App processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 20:14:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 May 2023 15:38:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 10 May 2023 04:23:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-11"}
