 of 90 natural product extracts on a microarray covering an area\nof less than 0.1 cm2. The arrays are suitable for miniaturized screening, for\ninstance in BSL-3 conditions where space is limited and for applications where\ncell numbers are limited, such as in functional precision medicine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 21:48:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-17"}
