erest for the final delensed\n$B$-mode power spectrum $l<l_{\\rm{cut}}$, similar to what was known previously\nfor the QE and the iterative estimator. We also present various NN training\ntechniques that can be extended for a simultaneous treatment of foregrounds and\nmore complex instrumental effects where the modeling is more uncertain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 22:17:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-17"}
