-induced electronic\nmodifications of the VO2 properties, as well as on nanoscale metal-oxide\ncontacts, which can help in the future design of oxide electronics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2022 23:08:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-24"}
