han other multimodal\ninformation. These entities are then integrated into the user-item interaction\ngraph. Afterwards, a symmetric linear Graph Convolution Network (GCN) module is\nconstructed to perform message propagation over the graph, in order to capture\nboth high-order semantic correlation and collaborative filtering signals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2022 01:09:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-17"}
