and inference than SN-kNN. The presented work analyzed the\ncharacteristics of both algorithms and image formats for the first time, thus\nproviding guidance for their future utilization in combustion monitoring tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2022 14:14:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2022 06:29:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-23"}
